{"tid":272740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係點學煮野食?","createTime":"2017-06-06T05:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T02:28:10.000Z","uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b27e36c43a00849db9835ca31d7808d596ad678","tid":272740,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"最近轉左新工有番多少少時間<br />\n想自學煮野食<br />\n大家有冇咩途徑自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0597e3ee6974fc5a0f5276cd8e25917a915a022","tid":272740,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"屋企人識煮嘅就得閒入廚房幫手<br />\n<br />\n無嘅就上網睇教學<br />\n<br />\n但最緊要係，唔好得個諗字講字(覺得你係)<br />\n<br />\n想煮就去煮，即刻行動，怕錯怕煮得唔好，就不如唔好學"},{"pid":"be819159545faed62e77a9daf308aa7822dd5479","tid":272740,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"最緊要落手煮<br />\n失敗幾次就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf9576af4895461275925cbfd98fae3dd30449a","tid":272740,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"落手落腳自己入廚房"},{"pid":"c378b1be7ccf8f3380c1ee661aceaf12b1eb0dfb","tid":272740,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"煮嘢食第一就一定係有嘢比你整<br />\n去街市學咗唔比d街市婆/佬滾九你先"},{"pid":"b8a001b7572b7fb81ae94241651500b29e1957f8","tid":272740,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"Ok 今晚開始入廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609648afe74d0b3b222ba494306a615f4e444379","tid":272740,"uid":72989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"我當年都係慢慢幫下手切嘢先，再煮下簡單嘢，再叫老母教。<br />\n<br />\n之後上網搵下食譜，整啲外國嘢，keep住個興趣先(我係鐘意煮唔同菜式嘅人嚟)<br />\n<br />\n同埋出街食到好西時可以留意多啲，返屋企還原到會好開心<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企廚房仔"},{"pid":"7374d7e6ccd83a31a724a3a932a0fcd77688c213","tid":272740,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"因為玩健身，加上係外國讀書，所以成日自己煮嘢食，煮到啲女仔都成日話邊個做我女朋友/老婆一定會好幸福，但係仍然係毒撚一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd5fe3b263b56f08f25d6238320d765ff533676","tid":272740,"uid":3713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:07:13.000Z","msg":"而家容易好多，想學乜上網都search到！"},{"pid":"b79096d755153bd2e013a4431901d0bb331d9ec6","tid":272740,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"以前有幫下老母切下菜 煮下飯<br />\n過時過節會包糭整蘿蔔糕<br />\n同自己得閒會整下蛋糕甜品<br />\n<br />\n而家自己1個人住 仲會帶飯<br />\n所以個個星期都會起碼煮2-3次<br />\n每次起碼3餸<br />\n有時fb碌到d recipe見幾得意又會試下煮<br />\n學到新菜式自己又鐘意食既話可以loop好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e640cf1833be38a9688db05344572bef63af24","tid":272740,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"老母教，好在老母識煮野食"}]}